Text: I want to move house to next door to her!

Haha, right on Poddington. The girl next door? In what fucking neighborhood, I want to move there.
Hell if I was in real estate I'd buy up a handful of houses & sell them at jacked up prices. Thats right, I'd say, you can get the same house for cheaper elsewhere but with girls like these living next door the property value skyrockets.
